<title type="html"><![CDATA[2/17 (Thu) Sitting is the new smoking / Are you ready for a 3D-printed house? (Host: Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=590&amp;p=613#p613"><![CDATA[
Sitting is the new smoking / Are you ready for a 3D-printed house?<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1<br />Sitting is the new smoking: ‘Truly a silent killer’<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.siouxfalls.business/sitting-is-the-new-smoking-truly-a-silent-killer/">https://www.siouxfalls.business/sitting ... nt-killer/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1. Would you take the research report seriously and share with<br />your family or friends?<br />2. How do you deal with sedentary problems if you need to sit all<br />day at the office?<br />3. Do you think you are an active person or an inactive person?<br />Are active people necessarily healthier than inactive people?<br />Why?<br />4. Do you know what’s the silent killer of mental health? Why?<br />5. Do you know what’s the silent killer of earth? Why?<br /> <br />Session 2<br />Are you ready for a 3D-printed house? They're cheaper, stronger and long-lasting<br />house? They’re cheaper, stronger and long-lasting, developers say<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.seattletimes.com/business/are-you-ready-for-a-3d-printed-house-theyre-cheaper-stronger-and-long-lasting-developers-say/">https://www.seattletimes.com/business/a ... opers-say/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1. We know 3D-printed house are cheaper, stronger and long- lasting, what are other advantages of this kind of house?<br />2. If you want to buy a house, would you like to buy 3D-printed or traditional house? Why?<br />3. Do you think 3D- printed house are the future of house? Why?<br />4. Since 3D printer can print a lot of items, if you have a printer,<br />what items will you print? Why?<br />5. Every year all kinds of new technology products come out, have<br />you ever tried some new products before? If so, please share with us.<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Feb 12, 2022 11:35 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
